AOS 96 is seeking a Central Office Bookkeeper. A degree in Accounting is preferred. Experience necessary in the following areas: accounts payable, payroll and Excel Spreadsheets. Knowledge of ADS software preferred. Competitive wages/Anthem Health Insurance. The position will be filled when a suitable candidate is found. Applications may be obtained at the Office of the Superintendent. You can also apply at ServingSchools.com.
Scott K. Porter
AOS 96
291 Court Street
Machias, ME 04654
(207) 255-6585
